![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6af38f48-6d39-4cdf-95a0-59c30daa567c/Screenshot_20240712_170459.jpg?format=original)

Tiffany Stratton opens Smackdown hyping herself as the youngest Ms. MITB in WWE history.

Bayley inturrupts to tell her if she even THINKS about cashing in, she'll be the first failed Ms. MITB.

Nia Jax comes out and says Bayley shouldn't be making empty threats and she should worry about their match at SummerSlam

Bayley says she isn't NXT hugger Bayley, she's not the Bayley that Nia Jax put on the shelf in 2017. This is the Grand Slam Women's Champion Bayley and she's going to beat Nia Jax at SummerSlam.

But if Bayley was to lose, what would Tiffany do when it's time to cash in?

Nia Jax says Tiffy is her personal little Barbie doll, she has no issues with Tiffy.

Tiffy and Nia jump Bayley until MICHIN comes out to save and clear the ring.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/481cd2d7-8fc6-4496-a9fe-77ec6a9e2b2d/Screenshot_20240712_171157.jpg?format=original)

