*   ## **_NAOMI DEF. BLAIR DAVENPORT_**
    

Decent match that ended up pretty clunky towards the end

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e5541b3c-90ec-4dde-9504-533d827f0f17/Screenshot_20240712_183056.jpg?format=original)

Naomi reunites with Jade and Bianca. They're happy for Bianca but they came to see Nick Aldis and he's not even here. They leave Naomi.

The people on front of Aldis office all get frustrated. Chelsea and Piper go in the office to see for themselves.

Blair Davenport comes up to Naomi. Offers respect and a handshake. Chelsea is back out and tells Naomi that Aldis really isn't here.

Davenport attacks Naomi from behind.

